{
  "stem": "21437.7",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're going to go on the death march, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- we heard bits and pieces here and there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a [GERMAN] where they sent-- sent some young people-- What's a-- what's a [GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A [GERMAN] means it was a room where they kept the-- the sick people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, you know, again you didn't want to go in the [GERMAN] because you knew that you were-- that you might disappear.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we had those-- suddenly we had those Hungarian girls who came from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came with shaven heads, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They was a-- they were just looked even worse than we did, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you had to the last minute, to the day before, you went-- we went away day before we went to work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eight of May.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Eight of May 1945.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On that day, we didn't hear-- in the morning, we didn't hear the sounds that, as horrible as they were, we were already familiar with.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So sometimes we just didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just-- there was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We just couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At least, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They just all up and left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They all run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, myself, if somebody said to me, look, you never know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We might survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This-- on this one thing, I kept answering the same way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Look, I know the mentality.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I hope that you are right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When somebody said something to me like this, I said, you know, I think would they want any witnesses really to what has happened?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So to me, anyhow, at certain moments, if I responded, I could respond in a positive way, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then I wanted-- you wanted to fool yourself a bit too, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
